---

### Request Body Parameters

| Field | Type | Required | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `amount` | number | ✅ | Amount to transfer (in RWF) |
| `phone` | string | ✅ | Recipient's phone number (e.g. `0798760888`) |
| `key` | string | ✅ | Your ITEC API key |

---

